<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang=”en”>
<head>
    <meta charset=”UTF-8”>
    <meta name=”viewport” content=”width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0”>
    <title>Your Name – Portfolio</title>
    <style>
        Body {
            Font-family: ‘Arial’, sans-serif;
            Margin: 0;
            Padding: 0;
            Background-color: #f4f4f4;
            Color: #333;
        }

        Header {
            Background-color: #333;
            Color: #fff;
            Text-align: center;
            Padding: 1em;
        }

        Section {
            Padding: 2em;
            Max-width: 1200px;
            Margin: 0 auto;
        }

        H1, h2, h3 {
            Color: #333;
        }

        .container {
            Width: 100%;
            Max-width: 1200px;
            Margin: 0 auto;
            Padding: 0 20px;
        }

        /* Responsive navigation menu */
        Nav {
            Display: flex;
            Justify-content: space-between;
            Align-items: center;
            Background-color: #333;
            Padding: 1em;
        }

        Nav a {
            Color: #fff;
            Text-decoration: none;
            Margin: 0 10px;
            Transition: color 0.3s;
        }

        Nav a:hover {
            Color: #ff9900;
        }

        /* Responsive layout */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            Nav {
                Flex-direction: column;
            }

            Nav a {
                Margin: 10px 0;
            }
        }

        /* Add your styles for other sections (About Me, Portfolio, Resume, Blog, Contact) here */

        Footer {
            Background-color: #333;
            Color: #fff;
            Text-align: center;
            Padding: 1em;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Your Name</h1>
        <p>Web Developer | Designer</p>
    </header>

    <!—Navigation 
    <nav>
        <a href=”#about”>About</a>
        <a href=”#portfolio”>Portfolio</a>
        <a href=”#resume”>Resume</a>
        <a href=”#blog”>Blog</a>
        <a href=”#contact”>Contact</a>
    </nav>

    <!—Sections 
    <section id=”about” class=”container”>
        <!—About Me content 
    </section>

    <section id=”portfolio” class=”container”>
        <!—Portfolio content 
    </section>

    <section id=”resume” class=”container”>
        <!—Resume content 
    </section>

    <section id=”blog” class=”container”>
        <!—Blog content 
    </section>

    <section id=”contact” class=”container”>
        <!—Contact content 
    </section>

    <footer>
        &copy; 2023 Your Name – Portfolio
    </footer>
</body>
</html>

```html
<!—Add this section inside the <body> element, before the header, after the navigation 
<nav class=”navigation”>
    <div class=”container”>
        <a href=”#about”>About</a>
        <a href=”#portfolio”>Portfolio</a>
        <a href=”#resume”>Resume</a>
        <a href=”#blog”>Blog</a>
        <a href=”#contact”>Contact</a>
    </div>
</nav>
```

And add the following CSS styles:

```css
<style>
    /* Add these styles inside the existing <style> tag */

    .navigation {
        Background-color: #333;
        Padding: 1em 0;
    }

    .navigation a {
        Color: #fff;
        Text-decoration: none;
        Margin: 0 20px;
        Font-size: 16px;
        Transition: color 0.3s;
    }

    .navigation a:hover {
        Color: #ff9900;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .navigation {
            Text-align: center;
        }

        .navigation a {
            Display: block;
            Margin: 10px 0;
        }
    }
</style>
```


